code: import faker from"faker";var generateUsers=function generateUsers(count){var users=[];for(var i=1;i<=count;i++){var firstName=faker.name.firstName();var lastName=faker.name.lastName();var attribute=faker.random.arrayElement(["社会人","学生"]);var email=faker.internet.email(firstName,lastName);var status=faker.random.arrayElement(["未登録","学生認証","承認","拒否","確認中"]);users.push({id:i,firstName:firstName,lastName:lastName,attribute:attribute,email:email,status:status});}return users;};export default generateUsers(30);
